creator: Dingi Technologies Limited
descriptionHtml:
One stop vehicle tracking solution


With tons of features you can choose, FollowR has the right solution tailored for your needs.

Live Tracking -Track your vehicle wherever it is with pinpoint accuracy.
Smart Geofencing - Get notified when your vehicle moves out of your preferred zone/route.
Facial Recognition Alarm - Get notified to any unauthorized access to your vehicle.
Incident Alarms - Real-time alarms and replays for incidents.
Driver Behavior Report - Automatic report of behaviors like harsh braking, overspeeding etc.
Track Multiple vehicle - Register and track more than one vehicles with just one user.
